metadata.name: Stranger #1
metadata.description: Welcome to the Age Of Strangers. A generative art NFT project composed of 5.000 hand drawn combinations by Dutch graphic artist Josie Boog. These individuals are lost in the digital world. They grew up in a world of division and conflict. They have lost sight of reality because of fear of missing out and over consuming digital content. Each Stranger is a unique, non-fungible token (NFT) on the Ethereum blockchain and gives the owner the right to participate in future activations of the AOS community. In the Age Of Strangers, scattering is natural, unifying is miraculous. Do you dare to be different? Become a Stranger and join the Age Of Strangers!
